Interface IncDes

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Ancestor, Blade, JASerializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Box, Bytes, Collection<ENTRY_TYPE>, Durable, FLenS<RESPONSE_TYPE>, JABoolean, JADouble, JAFloat, JAInteger, JAList<ENTRY_TYPE>, JALong, JAMap<KEY_TYPE,VALUE_TYPE>, JAString, MapEntry<KEY_TYPE,VALUE_TYPE>, Root, Tuple, Union, VLenS<RESPONSE_TYPE>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BList, BMap, BoxImpl, BytesImpl, CollectionImpl, DurableImpl, FLenScalar, IncDesImpl, IntegerBMap, IntegerSMap, JABooleanImpl, JADoubleImpl, JAFloatImpl, JAIntegerImpl, JALongImpl, JAStringImpl, LongBMap, LongSMap, MapEntryImpl, RootImpl, Scalar, SList, SMap, StringBMap, StringSMap, TupleImpl, UnionImpl, VLenScalar

    public interface IncDes
extends JASerializable, Blade, Ancestor
    IncDes is the interface for the durable part of all JASerializable objects.
